ActDepartment of Foreign Affairs and International Trade Act
SubjectEntente Canada-Québec relative au Programme de soutien au commerce mondial : Investissement Canada - Initiatives des communautés (ICIC) **AGREEMENT**
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Foreign Affairs conclude the Entente Canada-Québec relative au Programme de soutien au commerce mondial : Investissement Canada - Initiatives des communautés (ICIC). The purpose of the Agreement is to outline the partnership between the governments of Canada and Quebec to deliver the Global Commerce Support Program: Invest Canada - Community Initiatives (ICCI) to Quebec based communities.
